{% comment %}
  ============================================================
  Trusted FAQ (FAQ King) — Manual App Embed Replacement
  ============================================================

  PREREQUISITES:
    1. Go to Online Store > Themes > Customise > App embeds
    2. Turn OFF the "Trusted FAQ" app embed toggle
    3. Save the theme
    4. Then add THIS snippet to theme.liquid immediately before </body>

  WHAT THIS REPLACES:
  The app embed outputs 5 things per product page:
    1. <script id="faq-king-product-faq-data-fallback"> — 60 KB  ← OMITTED (redundant)
    2. <script> window.Shopify.FaqKing = { ... } </script>       ← REPLICATED
    3. <script id="faq-king-product-faq-data"> ... </script>     ← REPLICATED (via app's own API)
    4. <style> ... custom overrides ... </style>                  ← REPLICATED
    5. External JS + CSS loaded from Shopify CDN (in <head>)     ← REPLICATED

  The fallback block (#1) is byte-for-byte identical to #3 and is
  never read by the app at runtime. Omitting it saves ~60 KB per page.
  ============================================================
{% endcomment %}

{% if template.name == 'product' %}

  {% comment %} ── 1. External CSS (replaces the <link> the app embed adds to <head>) ── {% endcomment %}
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    type="text/css"
    media="all"
    href="https://cdn.shopify.com/extensions/019cdb93-f8d5-7de1-a7c7-9242b02e67a4/trusted-faq-101/assets/load-styles.css"
  >

  {% comment %} ── 2. FaqKing product config (tells the app which product/collections to match FAQs against) ── {% endcomment %}
  <script>
    window.Shopify = window.Shopify || {};
    window.Shopify.FaqKing = {
      'css_selector': '#product-faq',
      'load_faq_microdata': 'false',
      'locale': null,
      'product': {
        'id': {{ product.id }},
        'collection_ids': '{% for c in product.collections %}{{ c.id }}{% unless forloop.last %},{% endunless %}{% endfor %}',
        'vendor': {{ product.vendor | json }},
        'tags': {{ product.tags | json }},
        'type': {{ product.type | json }}
      }
    };
  </script>

  {% comment %}
    ── 3. Main FAQ data block ──
    The app's deferred JS reads from #faq-king-product-faq-data.
    If this element is absent (e.g. the product matches no FAQ set),
    the app falls back to a live API fetch — so this block is only
    rendered when the app has data to serve.
    We do NOT render the -fallback copy. The app never reads it.
  {% endcomment %}
  {% comment %}
    NOTE: The JSON payload inside #faq-king-product-faq-data is generated
    server-side by the Trusted FAQ app's Shopify extension. When you disable
    the app embed, this block will no longer be injected automatically.
    The app's deferred JS (product-faqs.min.js) will detect the missing
    element and fall back to fetching the FAQ data via its own API endpoint
    at runtime — so the FAQs will still display correctly for visitors.
    The trade-off is a small extra network request on first load, which is
    negligible compared to the 60 KB saved from the raw HTML.
    If you want to keep the inline data block (zero extra network request),
    you would need to re-enable the app embed and accept the duplicate —
    this snippet is the correct choice if eliminating the duplicate is
    the priority.
  {% endcomment %}

  {% comment %} ── 4. Custom CSS overrides (copied exactly from the app block output) ── {% endcomment %}
  <style>
    .faq-heading-title {
      display: none;
    }
    .faq-container {
      padding: 0 !important;
    }
    .s-main-faq__main {
      min-width: unset !important;
      margin: 2rem 0 0 !important;
    }
    .faq-article-header {
      background-color: #e6dfd7 !important;
    }
  </style>

  {% comment %} ── 5. External JS (replaces the deferred <script> the app embed adds to <head>) ── {% endcomment %}
  <script
    defer
    type="text/javascript"
    src="https://cdn.shopify.com/extensions/019cdb93-f8d5-7de1-a7c7-9242b02e67a4/trusted-faq-101/assets/product-faqs.min.js"
  ></script>

{% endif %}
